description:
  When the noise is deafening, can you really  
                 hear yourself?                

 Cast :  Tusshar Kapoor      Sendhil Ramamurthy
         Nikhil Dwivedi      Radhika Apte      
         Preeti Desai        Zakir Hussain     
         Girija Oak          Sundeep Kishan    
         Pitobash            Raja Sen          


    Director    :    Krishna D.K., Raj Nidimoru
    Writer      :    Krishna D.K., Raj Nidimoru
                     Sita Menon                

    Genre       :    Comedy | Crime | Drama    

 Shor In The City  movie revolves aroung three 
 stories in the midst of the noise of Mumbai.  
 The three stories run simultaneously but the  
 characters are not connected with each other. 
 Abhay, who is forced to come to an unwelcoming
 city, which he thought was home. Tilak is an  
 honest whisky peddler who gets crooked with   
 rowdy friends Ramesh and Mandook. They chance 
 upon a rare loot on a local train, which opens
 up new, dangerous avenues for them.           

